Welcome to White Star Corporations Data
", "desc": "
About the Server

White Star Corporations Data

White Star Corporations Data was created to log white star results in specially designated channels and threads.

Over time my skills improved and with the help of others I was able to build my own little empire. But I didn't do it alone; many people helped me, and the most important ones are described in the section below.

Our Discord Server

Our Discord server has channels for recording results, as well as the current status channel for active artefact boosts and a channel of statistics about white stars. You can also view them on the website.

Future Development

I want to continue developing this website, server, and bot, but I can't do it alone. Every suggestion and opinion counts!

  • Project Start Counter: Countup Since Project Start
  • Bots: R.T.S. and White Stars Mk2 were developed with the support of the Hades' Star Community Data database.
  • Automatic Translation: Authorize here to automatically translate messages mentioning you (@you) into your language.
